title: Midwestern Rainbows with Cameron Esposito
description:
Joe is joined by Cameron Esposito from the Seeso show Take My Wife as well as the hit ABC show A Million Little Things. Joe and Cameron chat about growing up in the Midwest and moving to the coasts to pursue their dreams before getting into emails from the fans.
